1. *Uživao* sam u predivnom zalasku sunca. (I enjoyed the beautiful sunset.)
2. On *uživa* u vožnji bicikla. (He enjoys cycling.)
3. *Uživala* sam u odličnoj hrani i društvu. (I enjoyed the great food and company.)
4. Oni *uživaju* u životu na selu. (They enjoy the life in the countryside.)
5. *Uživajte* u ovom predivnom danu! (Enjoy this beautiful day!)
6. On *je uživao* u predstavi sinoć. (He enjoyed the play last night.)
7. *Uživali* smo u vožnji na rolerima. (We enjoyed rollerblading.)
8. Ona *uživa* u plivanju. (She enjoys swimming.)
9. *Uživao* sam u čitanju ove knjige. (I enjoyed reading this book.)
10. On *će uživati* u putovanju po Evropi. (He will enjoy traveling around Europe.)